text: Tumegl/Tomils is a village in the municipality of Tomils of the district of Hinterrhein in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. In 2009 Tumegl/Tomils joined Feldis/Veulden, Scheid and Trans to become the municipality of Tomils. Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden
title: Tumegl/Tomils
